#. Tag: title
#: technical-reference.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "Technical References"
msgstr "Technische referentie"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktuberling; offers a gentle and rewarding introduction to &kde; "
"customization and programming. The application can be extended. For example, "
"without any coding, new playgrounds can be added by changing the graphics "
"files. By adding appropriate sound files, translators can change the sounds "
"to their native tongue!"
msgstr ""
"&ktuberling; biedt een elegante en belonende inleiding in het programmeren "
"voor en aanpassen van &kde;. Het programma kan worden uitgebreid. "
"Bijvoorbeeld, zonder dat u hoeft te programmaren kunt u nieuwe speelvelden "
"toevoegen door de grafische bestanden te wijzigen. Door de juiste "
"geluidsbestanden kunnen vertalers de geluiden aanpassen aan hun eigen taal!"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you extend or add to the game please consider sending your additions to "
"the maintainer <ulink url=\"mailto:alex@eyeos.org\">Alex Fiestas</ulink> for "
"inclusion in future releases."
msgstr ""
"Als u het spel uitbreidt, overweeg dan om uw toevoegingen te sturen aan de "
"onderhouder <ulink url=\"mailto:alex@eyeos.org\">Alex Fiestas</ulink> zodat "
"ze in toekomstige versies kunnen worden bijgesloten."

#. Tag: title
#: technical-reference.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "For Artists"
msgstr "Voor artiesten"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "To create a new &ktuberling; playground you have to:"
msgstr "Om een nieuwe &ktuberling; speelveld aan te maken dient u:"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draw the playground in a &SVG; file, there you have to:"
msgstr "Het te tekenen speelveld in een een &SVG;-bestand, waarin u:"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name the place where items can dragged <quote>background</quote>."
msgstr ""
"De plaats waar items naar toe gesleept worden <quote>background</quote> "
"wordt genoemd."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name each of the draggable items with an unique name."
msgstr "Geef elk van de versleepbare items een unieke naam."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a <literal role=\"extension\">.theme</literal> file, it has to follow "
"this schema:"
msgstr ""
"Maak een <literal role=\"extension\">.thema</literal>-bestand aan, met het "
"volgende schema:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: technical-reference.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lt;playground gameboard=\"<replaceable>yourSVGFile</replaceable>\" name="
"\"<replaceable>theDesktopFile</replaceable>\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;object name=\"<replaceable>itemName</replaceable>\" sound="
"\"<replaceable>soundName</replaceable>\" scale=\"<replaceable>someValue</"
"replaceable>\" /&gt;\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"&lt;/playground&gt;"
msgstr ""
"&lt;playground gameboard=\"<replaceable>uwSVGbestand</replaceable>\" name="
"\"<replaceable>hetBureaubladBestand</replaceable>\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;object name=\"<replaceable>itemNaam</replaceable>\" sound="
"\"<replaceable>geluidNaam</replaceable>\" scale=\"<replaceable>eenWaarde</"
"replaceable>\" /&gt;\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"&lt;/playground&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>yourSVGFile</replaceable> is the name of the &SVG; file that "
"has the drawing."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>uwSVGbestand</replaceable> is de naam van het &SVG;-bestand dat "
"de tekening bevat."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>theDesktopFile</replaceable> is the name of the desktop file "
"that has the name of the theme."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>hetBureaubladBestand</replaceable> is de naam van het "
"bureaubladbestand dat de naam van het thema bevat."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each object you need a <literal>&lt;object&gt;</literal> entry. "
"<replaceable>itemName</replaceable> is the unique name you used on the &SVG; "
"file, <replaceable>soundName</replaceable> is the sound name that will be "
"played when dragging it, see the <filename>sounds/soundthemes.HOWTO</"
"filename> file from source code for more information."
msgstr ""
"Voor elk object hebt u een <literal>&lt;object&gt;</literal>-item nodig. "
"<replaceable>itemNaam</replaceable> is de unieke naam die u gebruikt voor "
"het &SVG;-bestand, <replaceable>geluidNaam</replaceable> is de naam van het "
"geluid dat zal worden afgespeeld bij het slepen, zie het bestand "
"<filename>sounds/soundthemes.HOWTO</filename> uit de broncode voor meer "
"informatie."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>scale</literal> is optional and <replaceable>someValue</"
"replaceable> is the scale factor that will be used when drawing this object "
"outside the warehouse, if not specified is 1."
msgstr ""
"<literal>scale</literal> is optioneel en <replaceable>eenWaarde</"
"replaceable> is de schaalfactor die zal worden gebruikt bij het tekenen van "
"dit object buiten de opslagplaats, als deze niet is gespecificeerd dan is "
"deze 1."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> file, it has to "
"follow this schema:"
msgstr ""
"Maak een <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal>-bestand aan, met dit "
"schema:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: technical-reference.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[KTuberlingTheme]\n"
"Name=<replaceable>themeName</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"[KTuberlingTheme]\n"
"Name=<replaceable>themaNaam</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>themeName</replaceable> is the name that identifies the theme, "
"will be shown in the Playground menu."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>themaNaam</replaceable> is de naam die het thema identificeert "
"en zal worden getoond in het menu Speelveld."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are adding the theme to &ktuberling; repository, add <literal role="
"\"extension\">.svg</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">.theme</literal>, "
"and <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> files to <literal>FILES</"
"literal> section of the <filename>CMakeLists.txt</filename> into the "
"<filename class=\"directory\">pics/</filename> folder."
msgstr ""
"Als u het thema toevoegt aan de &ktuberling;-opslagruimte, voeg dan <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.svg</literal>-, <literal role=\"extension\">.theme</"
"literal>- en <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal>-bestanden toe "
"aan de sectie FILES van CMakeLists.txt in de map <filename class=\"directory"
"\">pics/</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to install it for yourself, place <literal role=\"extension\">."
"svg</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">.theme</literal>, and <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> files into the <filename class="
"\"directory\">ktuberling/pics</filename> folder in "
"<userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--paths GenericDataLocation</"
"option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Als u het wilt installeren voor uzelf, plaats <literal role=\"extension\">."
"svg</literal>-, <literal role=\"extension\">.theme</literal>- en <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal>-bestanden in de map <filename class="
"\"directory\">ktuberling/pics</filename> in <userinput><command>qtpaths</"
"command> <option>--paths GenericDataLocation</option></userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: technical-reference.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "For Translators"
msgstr "Voor vertalers"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides the usual <literal role=\"extension\">.po</literal> files mechanism "
"for translating program labels and prompts, the sounds can be localized too."
msgstr ""
"Naast de gebruikelijke mechanisme met <literal role=\"extension\">.po</"
"literal>-bestanden voor het vertalen van programmateksten en documentatie "
"kunnen ook de geluiden worden overgezet naar andere talen."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "To create a new &ktuberling; sound theme you have to:"
msgstr "Om een nieuw &ktuberling; geluid aan te maken dient u:"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Record the sounds in OGG Vorbis rc3 file format."
msgstr "Neem de geluiden op in OGG Vorbis rc3 bestandsformaat."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a <filename><replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable>."
"soundtheme</filename> file, it has to follow this schema:"
msgstr ""
"Maak een bestand <filename><replaceable>uwTaalTweeLetterCode</replaceable>."
"soundtheme</filename>, het moet dit schema volgen:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: technical-reference.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lt;language code=\"<replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable>"
"\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;sound name=\"<replaceable>soundName</replaceable>\" file="
"\"<replaceable>relativePath</replaceable>\" /&gt;\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"&lt;/language&gt;"
msgstr ""
"&lt;language code=\"<replaceable>uwTaalTweeLetterCode</replaceable>\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;sound name=\"<replaceable>geluidsNaam</replaceable>\" file="
"\"<replaceable>relatiefPad</replaceable>\" /&gt;\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"&lt;/language&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable> is your language two "
"letter code, for example gl for Galician."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>uwTaalTweeLetterCode</replaceable> is de twee lettercode van uw "
"taal, bijvoorbeeld nl voor Nederlands."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each sound a <literal>&lt;sound&gt;</literal> entry. "
"<replaceable>soundName</replaceable> should match with the soundName "
"specified in the playground theme (see the <filename>pics/themes.HOWTO</"
"filename> from source code). <replaceable>relativePath</replaceable> should "
"be the relative path you are going to install the file with this sound to, "
"typically it will be <filename><replaceable>someUniquePath</replaceable>/"
"<replaceable>soundName</replaceable>.<replaceable>format</replaceable></"
"filename> (<replaceable>someUniquePath</replaceable> can be your language "
"two letter code for example)."
msgstr ""
"Voor elke klank moet een <literal>&lt;sound&gt;</literal>-item. "
"<replaceable>geluidsNaam</replaceable> overeenkomen met de geluidsNaam "
"gespecificeerd in het playground-thema (zie de <filename>pics/themes.HOWTO</"
"filename> uit de broncode). <replaceable>relatievePad</replaceable> zou het "
"relatieve pad moeten zijn waar u het bestand met deze klank in gaat "
"installeren, dit is typisch <filename><replaceable>eenUniekPad</replaceable>/"
"<replaceable>geluidNaam</replaceable>.<replaceable>format</replaceable></"
"filename> (<replaceable>eenUniekPad</replaceable> kan bijvoorbeeld uw "
"tweeletterige taalcode zijn)."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are adding the sound theme to &ktuberling; in your language folder:"
msgstr "Als u het geluidsthema toevoegt aan de &ktuberling; in uw taalmap:"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add the sound files and the <literal role=\"extension\">.soundtheme</"
"literal> files into the <filename class=\"directory\">data/kdegames/"
"ktuberling</filename> folder of your language translations."
msgstr ""
"Voeg de klankbestanden en de <literal role=\"extension\">.soundtheme</"
"literal>-bestanden toe in de map <filename class=\"directory\">data/kdegames/"
"ktuberling</filename> van de vertalingen in uw taal."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On that very same dir you need a <filename>CMakeLists.txt</filename> file "
"describing how to install the files, typically it will be."
msgstr ""
"In diezelfde map hebt u een <filename>CMakeLists.txt</filename> nodig die "
"beschrijft hoe de bestanden te installeren, dit is typisch:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: technical-reference.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"FILE( GLOB oggfiles *.ogg )\n"
"INSTALL( FILES ${oggfiles} DESTINATION ${KDE_INSTALL_DATADIR}/ktuberling/"
"sounds/<replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable> )\n"
"INSTALL( FILES <replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable>."
"soundtheme DESTINATION ${KDE_INSTALL_DATADIR}/ktuberling/sounds/ )"
msgstr ""
"FILE( GLOB ogg-bestanden *.ogg)\n"
"install( FILES ${datafiles} DESTINATION ${DATA_INSTALL_DIR}/ktuberling/"
"sounds/<replaceable>uwTaalTweeLetterCode</replaceable> )\n"
"install( FILES <replaceable>uwTaalTweeLetterCode</replaceable>.soundtheme "
"DESTINATION ${DATA_INSTALL_DIR}/ktuberling/sounds/ )"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "If you want to install it for yourself:"
msgstr "Als u het wilt installeren voor uzelf:"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Place <filename><replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable>."
"soundtheme</filename> file into the <filename class=\"directory\">ktuberling/"
"sounds</filename> folder in <userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--"
"paths GenericDataLocation</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Plaats het bestand <filename><replaceable>uwTweeletterigeTaalcode</"
"replaceable>.soundtheme</filename> in de map <filename class=\"directory"
"\">ktuberling/sounds</filename> in <userinput><command>qtpaths</command> "
"<option>--paths GenericDataLocation </option></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Place your sound files into the <filename class=\"directory\">ktuberling/"
"sounds/<replaceable>someUniquePath</replaceable></filename> folder in "
"<userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--paths GenericDataLocation</"
"option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Plaats uw geluidsbestanden in de map <filename class=\"directory"
"\">ktuberling/sounds/<replaceable>eenUniekPad</replaceable></filename> in "
"<userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--paths GenericDataLocation</"
"option></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Information on how to work with the translation mechanisms in &kde; is "
"available in <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/docs/translation-howto/index."
"html\">The &kde; Translation HOWTO</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Informatie over hoe u gebruik kunt maken met de vertaalmechanismen van &kde; "
"is beschikbaar in <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/docs/translation-howto/"
"index.html\">The &kde; HOWTO voor vertalen</ulink>. Kijk ook op de "
"vertalerswebsite van het <ulink url=\"http://www.kde.nl/helpen/vertaling.html"
"\">Nederlandse KDE-team</ulink>."

